title: [The Ol' Switcheroo]
description: Dilapidated wooden planks make up this small seedy-looking booth, and a halfhearted attempt to mask the shoddy workmanship with a thin coat of noxious green paint only serves to make the squat structure uglier.  A table bridges the gap between the outside and the proprietor inside, whose voice continually rings out as he hawks his game.  A large banner drooping across the top of the wooden booth displays "The Ol' Switcheroo" in splotchy red letters.
